<template>

        <DataTable :value="kasaDetaylari" responsiveLayout="scroll" selectionMode="single">
            <Column field="ebat" header="Taş Ebatları"></Column>
            <Column field="kasaOlculeri" header="Kasa Ölculeri"></Column>
            <Column field="firmaadi" header="Firma Adı"></Column>
        </DataTable>


</template>
<script>
import service from '../../service/SeleksiyonService';
export default {
    components: {
      
    },
    created() {
        service.getKasaDetayOlculeri().then(data => {
            this.kasaDetaylari = data
        })
    },
    data() {

        return {
            kasaDetaylari: null,
            


        }
    },
    

}
</script>
